The paper discusses the security of robotic systems, which falls under the category of cyber security (cs.CR) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the design and architecture of the HoneyBot framework, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper uses machine learning techniques to analyze the data collected from the user study, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
